comments: Martin (MIA) collapses his arms as he establishes screening position and does not deliver illegal contact to Williams (CHI) as the pick is set.
Love (MIA) extends his arm outward and avoids making contact with DeRozan's (CHI) arm on the perimeter.
Butler (MIA) moves alongside White's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) avoids making body contact with Butler (MIA) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Love (MIA) and Dosunmu (CHI) mutually engage and incidental arm contact occurs as the two come during the pursuit of the rebound.
Martin (MIA) slightly drifts toward DeRozan (CHI) as he is drawn in the air by the pump fake and marginal leg contact occurs as DeRozan jumps to make a pass.
Love (MIA) extends and quickly retracts his left arm and avoids making contact with Vucevic's (CHI) arm during his upward shooting motion.
Martin (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position while defending DeRozan (CHI), who loses his balance on his own.
Butler (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from DeRozan (CHI) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Vucevic (CHI) slides his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Love (MIA) moves alongside Vucevic's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
White (CHI) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Butler's (MIA) arm.
